headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Teledyne Technologies (TDY) After Its Strong Multi‑Year Rally?
summary: If you are wondering whether Teledyne Technologies is priced attractively at its recent levels, the key question is how that share price lines up with the company’s underlying value. Over shorter and longer periods, the stock has seen returns of 6.0% over 7 days, 14.1% over 30 days, 12.1% year to date, 22.8% over 1 year, 43.9% over 3 years and 49.5% over 5 years.
